description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP discusses why he thinks Aaron Rodgers will stay in Green Bay. Tim Legler calls in and explains what he thinks Ben Simmons needs to be fixed. And Tim Cowlishaw shares some insight on Dak's surgery to fix his non throwing shoulder.
